OL,3,CD-Day veteran reflects on 'dreadful
OL,4,Csights' at Normandy landings
OL,6,FThe former soldier still vividly
OL,7,Fremembers the scene eighty years on.
OL,9,F"We saw this spectacle of thousands
OL,10,Fand thousands of ships, every type -
OL,11,Fbattleships, cruisers, destroyers,
OL,12,Flanding crafts.
OL,14,F"There were so many there you felt you
OL,15,Fcould walk across them without getting
OL,16,Fyour feet wet.
OL,18,F"I think to most of us, it was just an
OL,19,Fadventure - you didn't have time to be
OL,20,Fscared," he said.
