OL,3,CD-Day veteran reflects on 'dreadful
OL,4,Csights' at Normandy landings
OL,6,FSince 1994, John has only returned
OL,7,Fonce to the Normandy beaches - on the
OL,8,F75th anniversary of D-Day.
OL,10,F"I was looking along the gravestones
OL,11,Fin the war cemetery there, and just
OL,12,Ftaking note of the ages of some of the
OL,13,Flads and it was all 18, 19, early 20s.
OL,15,FIt always stuck in my mind that these
OL,16,Flads never experienced the privileges
OL,17,Fthat we had after we came home - of
OL,18,Fraising a family, getting a job and
OL,19,Feven living to a ripe old age as I've
OL,20,Fdone - these poor lads never
OL,21,Fexperienced that.
