OL,3,CD-Day veteran reflects on 'dreadful
OL,4,Csights' at Normandy landings
OL,6,F"I feel like it's my duty to pass on
OL,7,Finformation I can and give them an
OL,8,Finsight into what was is like and the
OL,9,Fgrief and that follows in its wake.
OL,11,FHe will mark the 80th anniversary of D-
OL,12,FDay by Attending a ceremony close to
OL,13,Fhis home in Peebles.
